<ptxt>
<emph>
P0500: Vehicle Speed Sensor &#8220;A&#8221;
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
This DTC is detected if any one of the following conditions is met.
</ptxt>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
VSS is lower than 2 km&#x002F;h (1.2 mile&#x002F;h) for 4 sec. when engine revolution is 3,600 rpm or less at fuel cut.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
VSS is lower than 2 km&#x002F;h (1.2 mile&#x002F;h) for 4 sec. when engine revolution is 3,700 rpm or more at D-range (A&#x002F;T model)
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
<ptxt>
(2 D&#x002F;C detection logic)
</ptxt>
</entry>
